"[RAD] is available for international roaming. After selecting the number from address call history or entering the number as usual, select Calling to Korea to create the intl call connecting number and country code (82) automatically for user convenience. ㅇRefer to the following for further details. ㅇCalling to Korea ㅇCalling to Others(Local/Overseas) ㅇCalling to T-Roaming Customer Service ㅇCalling to MFAT Call Center ㅇRAD SET and CANCEL"

"It is the same as calling in Korea, Enter the number or select the number from the address/call history. Select Calling to Korea. (Ex) Calling to 010-1234-5678 in Korea from Beijing, China: Enter 010-1234-5678 or select the number from the address or call history -> select Calling to Korea"

"▶Calling to Local: It is the local call to the country where the user is located. Enter the number or select the number from the call history -> Select Calling to Others(Ex) Calling to 133-1234-5678 in Beijing from Beijing, China: Enter 133-1234-5678 -> Select Calling to Others ▶Calling to Overseas: It is the overseas call excluded Korea and visited country. Enter the intl call connecting number and country code. Select Calling to Others. [Intl call connecting no.(press 0 for a certain time to be converted as +)-country code-receiver phone number(the first digit 0 excluded)-select Calling to Others] (Ex) Calling to 06-1234-5678 in Osaka, Japan from Beijing, China: Enter +81-6-1234-5678, Select Calling to Others"
Contact to T-Roaming Customer Service for the further information. Enter 114 on the keypad, select Calling to Korea to connect to T-Roaming CS (+82-2-6343-9011) automatically.

"This service is provided by the cooperation of Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade, which offers the consulate supporting services as follows. ◈Stolen/Lost Accident -contact number/report system to competent police office -reissuing passport/travel certificates, etc. ◈Injury/Death -Hospital and Interpretation Guide ◈Arrest/Detention -Contact to consul of Korea Embassy abroad -Attorney/Interpretation Guide, etc. Enter 112,113 or 119. Select Calling to Korea to connect to MFAT call center (+82-2-3210-0404) automatically."
"It can set/cancel RAD function. ▶ Set: Set RAD function ▶ Cancel: Cancel RAD function"
Roaming Local Time Guide Service Setting

[Roaming Local Time Guide Service] is the free service guiding the local time if the user calls to the party who uses intl roaming service. Contact to T-Roaming Customer Service for setup. Enter 114 on the keypad. Select Calling to Korea to connect to T Roaming CS (+82-2-6343-9011) automatically.
